Author: ddmar
Text: Ugh right? Also, like, why am I even hungry? I have like 100000 calories of body fat on me. Why can't my body just be satisfied with that?

Author: TotallyNotARadar
Text: Worse is when you try to engage in “self-care” and eat up to your low limit so you don’t actually die but that just makes you even hungrier and so now you feel full but also really want to binge
